00:12:46.080 --> 00:12:46.960
Ouille, aïe !

00:12:48.030 --> 00:12:50.160
Collier frite !

00:12:54.040 --> 00:12:55.090
Ma Douce arbelle.

00:12:55.790 --> 00:12:58.470
Es-tu satisfaite de ma prestation artistique ?

00:12:58.920 --> 00:13:01.250
Tais-toi, sale gibier de potence !

00:13:01.630 --> 00:13:04.220
Mais poussez-vous de là, bon sang !

00:13:06.100 --> 00:13:08.600
Salchow, reprends tes esprits !

00:13:08.760 --> 00:13:10.190
Arbelle...

00:13:11.640 --> 00:13:12.760
Vous avez pigé ?

00:13:12.940 --> 00:13:17.320
