00:14:21.670 --> 00:14:23.420
Regarde, j'ai une belle prise.

00:14:24.290 --> 00:14:27.050
Moi aussi, arbelle.

00:14:28.130 --> 00:14:29.510
La poisse...

00:14:30.380 --> 00:14:31.380
Smack !

00:14:39.110 --> 00:14:41.950
