00:15:14.630 --> 00:15:15.550
Jiro, fais pas ça.

00:15:21.390 --> 00:15:22.240
Pile comme prévu.

00:15:22.690 --> 00:15:23.270
Quoi ?

00:15:23.700 --> 00:15:24.950
Mon grand frère va venir.

00:15:25.740 --> 00:15:26.450
Ton frangin ?

00:15:28.270 --> 00:15:29.450
