00:18:31.720 --> 00:18:32.970
Non, luffy, derrière toi !

00:18:33.390 --> 00:18:34.180
Derrière ?

00:18:34.640 --> 00:18:35.890
Répulsion !

00:18:40.760 --> 00:18:42.230
