00:18:44.980 --> 00:18:45.800
Luffy !

00:18:46.300 --> 00:18:48.770
Gum gum... Rocket !

00:18:51.150 --> 00:18:52.490
Frangin !

00:18:52.950 --> 00:18:53.850
Luffy !

00:18:54.100 --> 00:18:54.950
La classe.

00:18:59.200 --> 00:19:00.200
Chapeau de paille...

00:19:02.030 --> 00:19:03.210
